      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a fantastic, reliable ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014it runs like a dream and has been well-loved! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it's totally ready for its next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable set of wheels that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
