    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver 333hp with a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Crucially, this example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: the rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates, the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells, and the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals and a cryo-treated hub. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the chassis's legendary lateral grip and steering feedback. While the Titan Silver metallic paint shows minor stone chips and the interior displays slight bolster wear, the drivetrain and structural integrity are exceptional. Documented service history included.",
